Package lt.viko.eif.vsubotkovski.companytoxml.models

Class Car

  • java.lang.Object
    • lt.viko.eif.vsubotkovski.companytoxml.models.Car
  • public class Car
extends Object
    Car class which consist of parameters that describe the car. Model, date of manufacture, price, engine, horse power, fuel type, gearbox, mileage, body type, number of doors, steering wheel, mot expiry, co2 emission.

    valde
